org.hkijena.jipipe.api

Class JIPipeGraphRunner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.api.JIPipeGraphRunner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable, JIPipeRunnable

    public class JIPipeGraphRunner
extends Object
implements JIPipeRunnable
    Executes an JIPipeGraph. This does not do any data storage or caching. Use this class for nested algorithm graph runs (like GraphWrapperAlgorithm) Use JIPipeProjectRun for full project runs.
